== [http://chromium-bsu.sourceforge.net Chromium B.S.U.] ==
[[File:Chromium-bsu_screenshot1.jpg|thumb|right|200px]]

Chromium B.S.U. is a classic arcade raster graphics vertical scrolling shoot 'em up single player game. It was written with games like [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raptor:_Call_of_the_Shadows Raptor] in mind and the idea to enhance them for modern graphics. As such it uses opengl via {{Package|media-libs/freeglut}} or alternatively sdl, supports fullscreen and modern audio themes.

