== [http://supertuxkart.sourceforge.net Supertuxkart] ==
[[File:Supertuxkart_screenshot1.jpg|thumb|right|200px]]

Supertuxkart is a free kart racing game starring Tux. It's a fork of TuxKart and under active development. It features single-player, multi-player and a story mode. You can choose from a lot of funny [http://supertuxkart.sourceforge.net/Characters characters] including Tux, Mozilla, Pidgin, Puffy and of course the GNU. There is also an addon manager integrated, you can find some addons [http://stkaddons.net here]. The gameplay combines regular kart racing with the possibility to collect items on the tracks with different properties (such as a cake bomb or a glue-like stuff to slow down opponents). You also have to look out for fuel items you can use to boost your speed for a short period of time. This makes the gameplay much more fun and reminds a bit of [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Super_Mario_Kart Super Mario Kart].

